1. open network setting and select ethernet adaptor then select properties
2. Pop up will show select Internet Protocol version 4(TCP/IPv4)
3. Click properties btn in popup
4. select Use the folloing IP address radio btn option
5. enter ip eg: 128.128.128.128
6. subnet automatically will come eg: 255.255.255.0
7. enter Defaultgatway eg : 198.168.1.1
8. enter your host provider DNS eg : 8.8.8.8
9. click ok
10. internet will work while browsing in browser but ping will not work
11 . to fix disable ipv6 in properties pop uncheck the ipv6 option and click ok
12. that's it
